<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-13-0629 </DOCNO><TEXT>In the first part of the report, the autors report on development tendenciesof the energy industry in the Federal Republic of Germany (primary energyconsumption; petroleum and gas imports; coal imports; electric powerconsumption; development of energy prices). The second part reports onthe results of the Conference of Ministers for Economic Affairs on 7thOctober 1987; and the third part explains and interprets the LEW-method(Lech Elektrizitaetswerke AG) of the Bavarian State Cartel Authority.The article closes with a summary of data relevant to energy economyin general.</TEXT></DOC>